      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential for precise torque distribution. The chassis is structurally immaculate with zero subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry remains perfectly dialed to factory specifications. The exterior paint retains its original depth and luster with no evidence of oxidation, while the cabin shows zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. A concours-level specimen for the discerning collector.",
