      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark, door ding, or stone chip. The interior remains in absolute showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear or creases, and the cabin remains smoke-free. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service performed on time and documented at the authorized dealership; the engine bay is pristine and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. Every electronic feature, from the high-resolution infotainment display to the multi-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. We are including both original key fobs, the factory owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive folder of service receipts. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the showroom floor.",
